#: TheoryHarmony/TheoryHarmony.cpp:58
msgid "A chromatic scale has the twelve notes, and each step of the scale is a semitone. Let's return to the piano keyboard. If you start on a C key and play every available key, black and white, until you arrive at the next C, you have played a chromatic scale:"
